00:00:00.951 --> 00:00:02.722
罗马之骄子下访此地
We are only too happy

00:00:02.747 --> 00:00:05.139
我们深感荣幸
to receive Rome's favored son.

00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:06.983
制造武器一举
The manufacture of armaments

00:00:07.008 --> 00:00:09.132
甚为挑衅
could be construed as a provocative move.

00:00:09.137 --> 00:00:11.673
我敢肯定宫廷之中藏有密探
I believe there may be a spy in my court.

00:00:11.742 --> 00:00:13.484
如果我们有什么事要通知你
If we have something to convey to you,

00:00:13.509 --> 00:00:17.203
则会刻字母欧米伽(Ω)
we will inscribe the letter Omega.

00:00:17.349 --> 00:00:20.691
告诉你们的教皇 不论是弗洛伦萨
Tell your Pope that neither Florence

00:00:20.716 --> 00:00:23.452
还是我达·芬奇都决不受他牵制
nor Da Vinci will be contained.

00:00:25.524 --> 00:00:27.592
无论这钥匙配的是什么样的锁
Whatever lock this corresponds with,

00:00:27.659 --> 00:00:31.063
我敢打赌 它必须和另外一把一起使用
I'd wager the key represents only half.

00:00:31.131 --> 00:00:33.032
缺了另一把钥匙 他的那一把便成不了事
The key is useless without its counterpart.

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:35.368
你听说过《叶之书》么?
Have you heard of the Book of Leaves?

00:00:35.436 --> 00:00:37.771
这只是个传说  和独角兽一样不可信
It's a myth. No more real than a unicorn.

00:00:37.839 --> 00:00:41.376
你和萨尔维亚蒂最好集合一切军力准备迎战
You and Salviati should assemble the largest army you can find.

00:00:41.444 --> 00:00:45.013
大师 去工作吧  佛罗伦萨就指望你了
Get to work, maestro. Florence is counting on you.

