00:48:29.579 --> 00:48:32.348
或是小尼克和我却没有得病呢
or young Nico, or myself fallen sick?

00:48:32.415 --> 00:48:34.984
是因为我们没有对雕像致意
It's because we made no obeisance to the statue.

00:48:35.052 --> 00:48:36.619
你和你的人也没有
Nor did you or your men.

00:48:36.687 --> 00:48:39.388
我一刻也无法容忍这种恶意的诽谤
I won't stand for this fatuous slander another moment.

00:48:39.456 --> 00:48:40.747
好吧 你只有一种办法去证明我是错的
Well, all you need to do is

00:48:40.748 --> 00:48:43.091
去亲吻圣安东尼的脚
kiss the feet of Saint Anthony to prove me wrong.

00:48:47.964 --> 00:48:50.932
麦角病
"Red ergot"?

00:48:51.000 --> 00:48:53.168
谁会听过这种东西
Who ever heard of such a thing?

00:48:53.236 --> 00:48:56.172
停下 我来告诉你
Stop! I will tell you.

00:48:56.240 --> 00:48:59.575
一位为杰弗瑞·德·布洛伊的历史学家
A historian by the name of Geoffroy du Breuil

00:48:59.643 --> 00:49:02.612
记录了12世纪的一次大肆虐
recorded one such outbreak in the 12th century.

00:49:02.680 --> 00:49:05.030
或许你就有它的副本
Perhaps you have a copy of it,

00:49:05.031 --> 00:49:07.851
藏在你的秘密卷宗里
hidden amongst your Secret Archives?

00:49:11.256 --> 00:49:13.690
此病有治愈方法
A treatment for this affliction exists.

00:49:13.758 --> 00:49:16.994
敷用这些草药和醋制成的绿色药膏
It's a green ointment of these herbs and vinegar,

00:49:17.061 --> 00:49:19.429
以及使用鲜活的水蛭给病人吸血
and a vigorous regime of leeching.

00:49:22.566 --> 00:49:24.379
我们用了此方 说不定还来得及
If we use this, we may still

00:49:24.380 --> 00:49:27.036
挽救那些病人性命
be able to save those who've fallen sick.

00:49:27.103 --> 00:49:29.238
干得好 达·芬奇
Well done, Da Vinci.

00:49:31.775 --> 00:49:33.142
谢谢你 大师
Thank you Maestro.

00:50:25.831 --> 00:50:27.364
你自己知道为何带我们来这
You know why you brought us here.

00:50:28.667 --> 00:50:31.202
我们用死来证明你的天赋
We died to prove your genius.

00:50:45.753 --> 00:50:48.454
里亚里奥
Riario!

00:51:09.376 --> 00:51:12.312
告诉我要说什么才能拿到另一把钥匙
Tell me what to say to win the other key.

00:51:12.379 --> 00:51:15.815
告诉我要说什么才能拿到那把钥匙
Tell me what to say to win the key!

00:51:15.883 --> 00:51:17.183
告诉我!
Tell me!

00:51:20.321 --> 00:51:24.524
我是大地与星空之子
I am a son of Earth and starry Heaven.

00:51:25.826 --> 00:51:30.729
我是大地与星空之子
I am a son of Earth and starry...

00:51:36.871 --> 00:51:38.371
妈妈
Mother?

00:51:46.848 --> 00:51:48.248
妈妈
Mother?

00:51:48.316 --> 00:51:51.585
达·芬奇 你听得到我说话么
Da Vinci... can you hear me?

00:51:51.653 --> 00:51:53.621
我觉得他有反应了
I think he's starting to respond.

00:52:01.597 --> 00:52:05.000
大师 你还好么?
Maestro...are you alright?

00:52:05.068 --> 00:52:08.470
你一直眼神呆滞 大喊大叫
You kept stirring and crying out.

00:52:08.538 --> 00:52:11.307
凡妮莎的唇
Vanessa's lips.

00:52:11.375 --> 00:52:14.977
凡妮莎的唇上 有麦角菌
Vanessa's lips... they bore the poison.

00:52:18.348 --> 00:52:20.749
- 我深陷幻觉   - 我们知道
- I was in a deep vision.   - Yes, we know.

00:52:20.817 --> 00:52:24.253
修女们已经为你治疗一整天了
The Sisters have been treating you all day long.

00:52:24.321 --> 00:52:27.623
凡妮莎 她痊愈了么
Vanessa? Is she - - Perfectly fine.

00:52:32.229 --> 00:52:35.765
你阻止了罗马虏获去一位美丽的受害者
You've kept Rome from claiming a beautiful victim.

00:52:35.833 --> 00:52:37.901
现在一切都结束了
It's all over now.

00:52:37.968 --> 00:52:40.503
对我来说 恐怕这才是个开始
For me, I fear it's just begun.

00:52:44.842 --> 00:52:46.576
"滚开 撒旦
"Begone Satan,

00:52:46.644 --> 00:52:48.245
经上记载
for it is written,

00:52:48.313 --> 00:52:50.787
你们应朝拜上主 敬奉上帝
you shall worship the Lord your God,

00:52:50.788 --> 00:52:52.850
仅听从上帝的指示"
and Him only shall you serve."

00:52:52.917 --> 00:52:54.685
你也熟知经文
You know your scripture.

00:52:54.753 --> 00:52:58.723
我现在知道很多事 主教大人
I now know a great many things, Cardinal.

00:53:01.727 --> 00:53:05.096
你应把这一口信传给里亚里奥
That's a message worth delivering to Riario.

00:53:05.164 --> 00:53:10.602
相信我 里亚里奥伯爵和我还有很多要探讨
Believe me, Count Riario and I have much to discuss.

00:53:17.142 --> 00:53:20.111
他们怎么做到的 大师?
How did they do it, Maestro?

00:53:20.179 --> 00:53:22.246
这不难
It wouldn't have been hard.

00:53:22.314 --> 00:53:27.118
正如院长所说 修道院为所有礼拜者开放
The Convent's open to all worshipers, as the Prioress said.

00:53:27.186 --> 00:53:30.488
随便一个颇富同情心的人 都可以信步走入
Just one single, sympathetic agent could have strolled in,

00:53:30.556 --> 00:53:34.726
在圣安东尼的脚趾上撒毒
contaminated the toes of Saint Anthony...

00:53:34.794 --> 00:53:38.863
然后静静等待
..And waited.

00:53:38.931 --> 00:53:43.634
深渊与深渊响应
And then Abyssus abyssum invocat

00:53:43.702 --> 00:53:45.736
一着不慎 满盘皆输
One misstep leads to another.

00:54:09.095 --> 00:54:12.531
他们对虔诚的信徒下了毒
They poisoned the pious.

00:54:12.598 --> 00:54:15.700
主啊 可怜可怜这些信徒吧
Oh, God, have mercy on the believers.

00:54:15.768 --> 00:54:18.603
我们为佛罗伦萨争取了更多的时间
We just bought Florence more time.

00:54:24.677 --> 00:54:27.478
- 怎么了   - 一个骑手带来话
- What is it? - A rider brought word.

00:54:27.546 --> 00:54:30.848
你弟弟一不小心把咱们的军火数量说漏了
Your brother let slip how many guns we have.

00:54:30.916 --> 00:54:33.150
虽说武器还在生产 但
Production continues, but...

00:54:33.218 --> 00:54:35.219
朱利亚诺本可设法蒙蔽他们 可他却承认了
Giuliano could've hidden his error but admitted it.

00:54:35.287 --> 00:54:37.455
瞧他干的好事
For all the good that does.

00:54:37.523 --> 00:54:41.759
摸清底细之后 罗马会立刻发起进攻的
Rome will strike when it knows exactly what it faces.

00:54:41.827 --> 00:54:44.028
我们现在要生产更多炮火
We'll have to produce even more guns now.

00:54:46.298 --> 00:54:47.670
对 我叫人搜遍了整个宫殿
Oh, yes, I ordered a full

00:54:47.671 --> 00:54:49.867
不放过任何角落
search of the palace, no stone unturned.

00:54:49.934 --> 00:54:51.201
你有什么发现么?
Have you discovered something?

00:54:51.269 --> 00:54:53.903
可能我们应该私下讨论
Perhaps we should discuss this in private.

00:54:53.971 --> 00:54:58.939
现在就给我看 孔蒂
Show me now, Conti, or

00:54:58.940 --> 00:55:08.651
否则我就认为是你在掩饰什么
I'll think it's you with something to hide.

00:55:08.719 --> 00:55:10.220
你在哪找到的这个
Where did you find this?

00:55:10.287 --> 00:55:12.489
哪里
Where?

00:55:12.556 --> 00:55:14.124
在贝奇大人的住处
In Signor Becchi's quarters.

00:55:14.191 --> 00:55:16.092
你撒谎
You lie!

00:55:16.160 --> 00:55:17.861
这些不是我的
These are not mine!

00:55:17.929 --> 00:55:20.397
我是在架子上找到的 大人 我发誓
It was on a shelf, il Magnifico. I swear.

00:55:20.464 --> 00:55:22.132
藏于其他书籍之间
Hidden amongst other books.

00:55:22.199 --> 00:55:26.537
是你
It was you.

00:55:26.604 --> 00:55:28.271
自始至终 叛徒都是你
All along, the traitor was you.

00:55:28.339 --> 00:55:30.340
洛伦佐 这是个误会
Lorenzo, this is a mistake.

00:55:30.408 --> 00:55:32.742
罗马斯库多
Roman Scudos.

00:55:32.810 --> 00:55:34.177
印有罗马教宗封印的纸张
Papers with the Papal Seal.

00:55:34.245 --> 00:55:38.782
送往罗马的情报掩藏地
A list of locations to hide them for delivery to Rome.

00:55:38.849 --> 00:55:42.286
家贼难防啊
Found in my home!

00:55:42.353 --> 00:55:44.021
- 不要怀疑我 洛伦佐   - 闭嘴
- Please, Lorenzo... - Silence!

00:55:44.088 --> 00:55:46.256
否则我会亲自割下你的舌头
Or I'll cut out your tongue myself.

00:55:50.428 --> 00:55:51.628
把他带走
Remove him.

00:55:56.501 --> 00:55:58.235
交给巴杰罗处置
To the Bargello.

00:56:01.606 --> 00:56:03.474
看来你好像又赢了
It would appear you've won again.

00:56:05.344 --> 00:56:08.345
一盘结束 一盘又始
There will be other games.

00:56:08.413 --> 00:56:11.949
选择要走的路
It's difficult, choosing which path to follow,

00:56:12.017 --> 00:56:17.255
试图透过精心设计的策略看到光明大道 这很难
trying to see a way through all the strategies you've initiated.

00:56:17.322 --> 00:56:19.023
不
No.

00:56:19.091 --> 00:56:22.360
不 那不难
No, that's not difficult.

00:56:22.428 --> 00:56:25.663
只要有信仰便可
You simply have to believe.

00:56:25.731 --> 00:56:28.700
以我之见 信仰绝不简单
In my experience, there's nothing simple about belief.

00:56:28.767 --> 00:56:31.503
这就是你我的不同之处
That's the difference between you and me.

00:56:34.507 --> 00:56:35.774
不同之处 不仅一个
Not the only one.

00:56:50.024 --> 00:56:52.892
我听到你叫我了
I heard you.

00:56:52.960 --> 00:56:54.627
告诉佐 把这些尸体处理掉
Tell Zo to dispose of these.

00:56:54.695 --> 00:56:56.362
我已研究完毕
They've served their purpose.

00:57:01.335 --> 00:57:05.471
它好像很喜欢待在这儿 不是么
I gather he quite prefers it in there, no?

00:57:07.974 --> 00:57:10.543
它好像不想获得自由
He doesn't seem to be interested in his freedom,

00:57:10.610 --> 00:57:13.312
大概时候因为它喜欢这漂亮的笼子
maybe he likes his pretty cage.

00:57:29.262 --> 00:57:32.564
鬼火
Ignis fatuus.

00:57:42.342 --> 00:57:46.212
一盘结束 一盘又始
As one game ends, another begins.